  <!-- ═══ FAQ ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center reveal">
        <span class="section-label">Common Questions</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin: 0 auto;">Everything you need to know before your purchase. Can't find an answer? Our team is one message away.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-grid">

        <div class="faq-item reveal" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>How long does delivery take?</h3>
            <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
          </div>
          <p class="faq-answer">Standard delivery takes 5–7 business days across the continental US. Our white-glove delivery service — included free on orders over $500 — includes in-home assembly and packaging removal, typically within 7–10 business days.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item reveal" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>What does the 12-year warranty cover?</h3>
            <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
          </div>
          <p class="faq-answer">Our warranty covers all mechanical components (tilt mechanism, gas lift, armrest mechanisms), the aluminum base, and the mesh fabric against manufacturing defects. Cosmetic wear from normal use is not covered. Warranty transfers to new owner if the product is resold.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item reveal" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>Can I try a chair before I buy?</h3>
            <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
          </div>
          <p class="faq-answer">Absolutely. We offer a 30-day home trial on all chairs. If you're not completely in love with your FORMA chair, simply contact us and we'll arrange a free return pickup, no questions asked. We also have showrooms in New York, Los Angeles, and London for in-person demonstrations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item reveal" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>Do you offer corporate or bulk pricing?</h3>
            <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
          </div>
          <p class="faq-answer">Yes! Orders of 10 or more chairs qualify for our corporate pricing program, with discounts starting at 15%. We also offer a dedicated account manager, custom branding on select products, and priority lead times. Contact our enterprise team for a custom quote.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item reveal" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>Is financing available?</h3>
            <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
          </div>
          <p class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer 0% APR financing for 12 months on approved credit applications through our partner, Affirm. Monthly payments start as low as $49/month. You can select financing at checkout, and approval takes under 2 minutes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item reveal" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>Are FORMA products environmentally friendly?</h3>
            <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
          </div>
          <p class="faq-answer">Sustainability is at the core of how we build. Our frames use certified recycled aluminum, our mesh fabrics are OEKO-TEX Standard 100 certified, and our packaging is 100% recyclable. We are also carbon-neutral certified through our partnership with Gold Standard projects.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
